{"tid":676581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"農夫唱到去德國 陸永：邊個黎睇？","createTime":"2018-05-24T13:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T02:26:18.000Z","uid":82917,"like":1563,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"f112adac7fbf8019e2fef55a858b8b368e66aa65","tid":676581,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IwyRCLNVwYE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIwyRCLNVwYE&d=4ZVudcRlPp7XFGcZfqAsVf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5fe6c4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IwyRCLNVwYE</a><br />\n<br />\n組合農夫昨日在將軍澳擔任開幕嘉賓，剛在澳門開完巡迴演唱會的兩人，稍後會到東南亞及內地開騷，陸永坦言沒想過連德國都邀請他們：「德國都有人睇我哋，做到都開心，不過我哋唔會唱英文歌，入場睇我哋應該都唔會係德國人，不過會學幾句打招呼。」他更反問：「到底乜人會嚟睇？<span style=\"color: red;\">唔通睇樣咩？真係未見過咁靚嘅人類。</span>」<br />\n做巡迴演唱會做到去德國，不過農夫否認賺得多，笑問兩人賺多了幾多個零？陸永搞笑地說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">來來去去咪又係鄭裕玲，一個鄭裕玲都夠啦！</span>」C君附和說：「如果鄭裕玲肯畀個零我，我哋唔走㖭喇！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正呀fama<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好想嫁比農夫系列</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a3dacfc3065d38ab21f4f11b193b523da3a7d0","tid":676581,"uid":82917,"like":660,"dislike":9,"score":651,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"轉數真係好撚快，抵佢地食呢行飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a38593158e4f88c2584f0185ca0c2eed57fad4","tid":676581,"uid":38904,"like":512,"dislike":5,"score":507,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"識自嘲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵佢撈得掂<img src=\"/assets/face